  "headline": "Immune System Boosters",
  "description": "Immune system 'boosters' are largely lifestyle factors, not supplements. Evidence-based: adequate sleep, regular moderate exercise, stress management, balanced diet (zinc, vitamin C, D), not smoking, moderate alcohol. 'Boosting' the immune system is a marketing myth — you want balanced, not overactive (allergies, autoimmunity).",
